  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i1.s.hjfile.cn/entry/201506/3761af7f-e153-48fe-bebd-ef22dd6e53b9.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p779801\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tHow will the European Union react to major challenges to its <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/authority\" target=\"_blank\">authority</a> from its north and south? That's the question European leaders are having to <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/grapple\" target=\"_blank\">grapple</a> with again after another difficult week. Today Greece upped the stakes in its negotiations over a new <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/bailout\" target=\"_blank\">bailout</a> deal. It was due to make a 300-million-dollar <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/repayment\" target=\"_blank\">repayment</a> to the IMF by the end of the day. But in an unprecedented move it's chosen to roll this and other payments over till the end of the month. It's been seen as a political decision and an attempt to pile pressure on the country's creditors. Well in the last few minutes the Greek Prime Minister Alexis Tsipras has begun addressing the Greek parliament.</p>\n<p>\n\tWell further north the British Prime Minister David Cameron is trying to drum up support for <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/fundamental\" target=\"_blank\">fundamental</a> reform of the EU. He's promised an in-out <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/referendum\" target=\"_blank\">referendum</a> by the end of 2017. And he says that without change Britain might decide to leave the EU altogether. It won't be the first time British voters have been asked about the country's future in Europe. On June 6th, 1975, 40 years ago tomorrow, voters were also asked directly whether Britain should remain in what was then called the Common Market.</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江</span><a>英语</a><span>&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。&gt;&gt;<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/course/52569?source=16553\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\">零基础直达流利生活口语班</a>&lt;&lt;</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p779801/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p779801\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p784513/\">魔兽世界上映！游戏神还原+吴彦祖 给满分！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p783222/\">老外爆料办公室的奇葩规定：第1条你就笑了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p783901/\">《X战警：天启》11个彩蛋全解析！看完给跪</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p784384/\">猴年马月真的来啦！英文要怎么说？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p783729/\">对自己好一点：当你爱自己时是什么样子？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p784434/\">囧研究：为啥初为人母的妈喜欢在朋友圈晒娃</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p783658/\">老外告诉你：什么时候该“被动”？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p783739/\">跑半马的小伙子意外走红 照片已被玩坏</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p784397/\">今年高考的各种作文题 老外是这么hold住的</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p745339/\">7个小技巧教你穿出质感 高端大气上档次</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=